## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or recent scholarly research on the topic. Additionally, the historical accounts of resistance are often derived from records kept by enslavers, which may not fully capture the experiences and strategies of the enslaved. Further research, including primary source analysis, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the diverse forms of resistance to slavery.